Problem Statement: Telecom Network Anomaly Detection
Objective
Design and implement an automated data processing system that continuously monitors telecom network performance metrics and detects anomalies in near real-time to ensure service reliability and quality.

Background
==============
Telecom operators like Airtel, Jio, and Vodafone Idea manage thousands of network towers and infrastructure components.

Each tower generates continuous data such as:
Latency (network delay)
Packet loss (data reliability)
Throughput (data speed)

Unexpected deviations in these metrics can indicate:
Network congestion
Hardware failures
Signal degradation
Service outages

Problem
Manual monitoring of such large-scale data is:
Not scalable
Error-prone
Slow to react

There is a need for an automated system that can:
Process raw telecom data (CSV, JSON, logs)
Detect abnormal patterns (anomalies)
Generate actionable reports
Enable faster decision-making


Key Requirements
------------------
1. Data Ingestion
Read telecom KPI data from:
CSV files
JSON APIs
Log files

2. Data Processing
Clean and normalize inconsistent data
Handle missing or noisy values
Convert raw logs into structured format

3. Feature Engineering
Extract meaningful metrics:
Average latency per tower
Packet loss trends
Throughput distribution

4. Anomaly Detection
Identify unusual patterns using:
Statistical thresholds (rule-based)
Machine learning models (e.g., Isolation Forest)

5. Output Generation
Produce:
Structured reports (CSV/JSON)
Summary dashboards
Alerts for anomalies

6. Automation
Run the pipeline:
Periodically (cron jobs)
Or in real-time (streaming systems)

Expected Output
List of anomalies with timestamps
Tower-wise health status
Aggregated performance metrics
Final report for operations team

Success Criteria
Detect anomalies with high accuracy
Reduce detection time from hours → seconds/minutes
Enable proactive network maintenance
Improve overall Quality of Service (QoS)

Real-World Impact
This system helps telecom companies:
Prevent outages before customers notice
Optimize network performance
Reduce operational costs
Improve customer experience

One-Line Summary
Build an automated pipeline that transforms raw telecom data into actionable insights by detecting network anomalies efficiently.
